      <p><strong>Key Point 2 вҖ” Theological Frame:</strong> Similarities exist because Muhammad (PBUH) was familiar with Judeo-Christian apocalyptic traditions, and Islamic eschatology built on and corrected those traditions. The common themes reflect a shared Abrahamic framework вҖ” not a sinister convergence.</p>
